<div style='direction:ltr;border-width:100%'>

<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:8.4708in'>

<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:8.4708in'>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>缓存是内存当中一块存储数据的区域，目的是提高查询效率。</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>会将查询结果存储在缓存当中，当下次执行相同的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SQL</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>时不访问数据库，而是直接从缓存中获取结果，从而减少服务器的压力。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中缓存分为一级缓存（本地缓存）和二级缓存。缓存查询数据的顺序是：</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"' lang=zh-CN>二级缓存——</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"' lang=zh-CN>&gt;</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei UI"' lang=zh-CN>一级缓存——</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'
lang=zh-CN>&gt; </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'
lang=zh-CN>数据库。</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>在对数据库的一次会话（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>）中，我们有可能会反复地执行完全相同的查询语句，如果不采取一些措施的话，每一次查询都会查询一次数据库</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>,</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>而我们在极短的时间内做了完全相同的查询，这有可能造成很大的资源浪费，因为它们的结果极有可能完全相同。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>为了解决这一问题，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>会在一次会话（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）中，一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>对象中创建一个本地缓存</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>(local
     cache)</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>，对于每一次查询，都会尝试根据查询的条件去本地缓存中查找是否在缓存中，如果在缓存中，就直接从缓存中取出，然后返回给用户；否则，从数据库读取数据，将查询结果存入缓存并返回给用户</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=338 height=151></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>每当我们使用</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>开启一次和数据库的会话（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>），</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>会创建出一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>对象表示一次数据库会话。在同一个会话（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）里面，多次执行相同的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>语句，会直接从内存取到缓存的结果，不会再发送</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>到数据库。不同的会话（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）里面，即使执行的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SQL</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN><span
     style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span></span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>一模一样（通过一个</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Mapper </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的同一个方法的相同参数调用），也不能使用到一级缓存</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>使用一级缓存的时候，因为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession
     </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>的实例线程不是安全的，因此是缓存不能跨会话共享，不同的会话之间对于相同的数据可能有不一样的缓存。在有多个会话或者分布式环境下，会存在脏数据的问题。如果要解决这个问题，就要用到二级缓存。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:black'
     lang=zh-CN>二级缓存是比一级缓存作用范围更广的缓存，二级缓存可以通过</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>cache-ref</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>让多个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>mapper.xml</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>共享一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>namespace</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，从而实现了跨会话（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）的缓存共享。</span></li>
</ul>
